red in a video library for FloTrack subscribers to watch for the duration of their subscriptions.\", \"from\": 3042, \"to\": 3193, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tags:  Get the most important Track & Field stories delivered straight to your inbox.\", \"from\": 3195, \"to\": 3280, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3225, \"end\": 3238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Track_and_field\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.152856939844909e-58, \"text\": \"Track & Field\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Track_and_field\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Track_and_field\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a92006 - Present FloSports, Inc. All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 3282, \"to\": 3334, \"entities\": []}]}"